        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h6 id="相关文档"><a href="#相关文档" class="headerlink" title="相关文档"></a>相关文档</h6><p><a href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo webpage</a> <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/">Documentation</a>  <a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues">GitHub</a> <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html">Writing</a></p><h6 id="基本命令"><a href="#基本命令" class="headerlink" title="基本命令"></a>基本命令</h6><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new your-blog-title</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="尝试加入图片-需要将图片放入-source-images路径下"><a href="#尝试加入图片-需要将图片放入-source-images路径下" class="headerlink" title="尝试加入图片 需要将图片放入&#x2F;source&#x2F;images路径下"></a>尝试加入图片 需要将图片放入&#x2F;source&#x2F;images路径下</h5><p><img src="/../images/test/wallhaven-7pqyqe.jpg"></p><p>pass word只需要在前面YMAL Front Matter中加入 password: ….即可</p>]]></content>
      
      
